# Nodo Serrano Landing Page - Cursor Rules

## Project Overview
Nodo Serrano is a landing page for an Ethereum community initiative in Tandil, Argentina. It serves as a "Hackerspace y Semillero" (Hackerspace and Seedbed) focused on Ethereum research and education. The site features newsletter subscription, event information, and a blog system.

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 16 with App Router (React 19)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS with custom neumorphism design system
- **UI Components**: shadcn/ui with Radix UI primitives
- **Database**: Neon PostgreSQL (serverless)
- **Animations**: Framer Motion
- **Content**: Markdown-based blog with remark/rehype processing
- **Email**: Nodemailer for notifications
- **Deployment**: Vercel with automatic deployments via GitHub Actions

## Architecture

### Frontend Structure
```
app/                          # Next.js App Router
├── layout.tsx               # Root layout with Inter font
├── page.tsx                 # Main landing page
├── globals.css              # Custom neumorphism CSS system
├── actions.ts               # Server actions (newsletter)
└── api/                     # API routes
    ├── subscribers/         # Newsletter subscription API
    ├── blog/               # Blog content APIs
    └── health/             # Health check

components/                  # React components
├── ui/                     # shadcn/ui components
├── svgs/                   # Custom SVG components
└── [feature components]    # Page-specific components
```

### Backend & Data
```
lib/                        # Utility libraries
├── db.ts                  # Neon database connection
├── blog/                  # Blog processing system
│   ├── markdown.ts        # MDX processing with syntax highlighting
│   ├── schema.ts          # Zod validation schemas
│   └── static-data.ts     # Build-time data generation
├── email.ts               # Email notification system
└── [other utilities]
```

### Content Management
```
content/blog/              # Markdown blog posts
database/schema.sql        # PostgreSQL schema
```

## Design System

### Neumorphism Theme
The site uses a custom neumorphism design system with layered backgrounds:
- `layer0`: Darkest (#1a1c20) - page/section backgrounds
- `layer1`: Medium (#1e2024) - neumorphism containers
- `layer2`: Light (#26282C) - nested containers
- `layer3`: Lightest (#2e3034) - deeply nested containers

### Color Palette
Custom cyan, violet, and blue color schemes with extended ranges (50-900), plus shadcn/ui CSS variables for theming.

### Typography
- **Primary Font**: Inter (Google Fonts)
- **Fallback**: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif
- **Content**: @tailwindcss/typography for prose

